 European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{Official URL}}\n| footnotes               =\n}}\nThe '''Municipality of Sevnica''' ({{IPA-sl|\u02c8se\u02d0u\u032fnitsa|pron|Sevnica.ogg}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Sevnica}}) is a [[Municipalities of Slovenia|municipality]] along the [[Sava]] and the [[Mirna (Sava)|Mirna]] Rivers in southeastern [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Sevnica]]. Today it is part of the [[Lower Sava Statistical Region]]. It is the 12th-largest municipality by area in Slovenia.<ref name=\"SORS-MUN-SEVNICA\">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.si/ObcineVStevilkah/Vsebina.aspx?leto=2012&id=149&lang=eng |title=Municipality of Sevnica |publisher=Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia |accessdate=5 September 2012 |work=Place Names}}</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the namesake town, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n* [[Apnenik pri Bo\u0161tanju]]\n* [[Arto, Sevnica|Arto]]\n* [[Birna Vas]]\n* [[Blanca, Sevnica|Blanca]]\n* [[Bo\u0161tanj]]\n* [[Breg, Sevnica|Breg]]\n* [[Brezje, Sevnica|Brezje]]\n* [[Brezovo, Sevnica|Brezovo]]\n* [[Budna Vas]]\n* [[\u010canje]]\n* [[\u010celovnik]]\n* [[Cerovec, Sevnica|Cerovec]]\n* [[\u010ce\u0161njice, Sevnica|\u010ce\u0161njice]]\n* [[Dedna Gora]]\n* [[Dolenji Bo\u0161tanj]]\n* [[Dolnje Brezovo]]\n* [[Dolnje Impolje]]\n* [[Dolnje Orle]]\n* [[Dro\u017eanje]]\n* [[Dru\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Gabrijele]]\n* [[Gabrje, Sevnica|Gabrje]]\n* [[Gornje Brezovo]]\n* [[Gornje Impolje]]\n* [[Gornje Orle]]\n* [[Goveji Dol]]\n* [[Hinjce]]\n* [[Hinje, Sevnica|Hinje]]\n* [[Hudo Brezje]]\n* [[Jablanica, Sevnica|Jablanica]]\n* [[Jelovec, Sevnica|Jelovec]]\n* [[Jeperjek]]\n* [[Kal pri Krmelju]]\n* [[Kamenica, Sevnica|Kamenica]]\n* [[Kamen\u0161ko]]\n* [[Kaplja Vas, Sevnica|Kaplja Vas]]\n* [[Kladje nad Blanco]]\n* [[Kladje pri Krmelju]]\n* [[Koludrje]]\n* [[Kompolje, Sevnica|Kompolje]]\n* [[Konjsko, Sevnica|Konjsko]]\n* [[Krajna Brda]]\n* [[Kri\u017e, Sevnica|Kri\u017e]]\n* [[Kri\u017ei\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Krmelj]]\n* [[Krsinji Vrh]]\n* [[Laze pri Bo\u0161tanju]]\n* [[Ledina]]\n* [[Leskovec v Podbor\u0161tu]]\n* [[Log, Sevnica|Log]]\n* [[Loka pri Zidanem Mostu]]\n* [[Lon\u010darjev Dol]]\n* [[Lukovec, Sevnica|Lukovec]]\n* [[Mala Hubajnica]]\n* [[Malkovec]]\n* [[Marendol]]\n* [[Metni Vrh]]\n* [[Mrtovec]]\n* [[Mrzla Planina]]\n* [[Novi Grad, Sevnica|Novi Grad]]\n* [[Okroglice]]\n* [[Orehovo]]\n* [[Ore\u0161je nad Sevnico]]\n* [[Osredek pri Hubajnici]]\n* [[Osredek pri Krmelju]]\n* [[Otavnik]]\n* [[Pavla Vas]]\n* [[Pe\u010dje]]\n* [[Pijavice]]\n* [[Podbor\u0161t, Sevnica|Podbor\u0161t]]\n* [[Podgorica, Sevnica|Podgorica]]\n* [[Podgorje ob Sevni\u010dni]]\n* [[Podvrh, Sevnica|Podvrh]]\n* [[Poklek nad Blanco]]\n* [[Polje pri Tr\u017ei\u0161\u010du]]\n* [[Ponikve pri Studencu]]\n* [[Preska, Sevnica|Preska]]\n* [[Pre\u0161na Loka]]\n* [[Primo\u017e, Sevnica|Primo\u017e]]\n* [[Ra\u010dica, Sevnica|Ra\u010dica]]\n* [[Rade\u017e]]\n* [[Radna, Sevnica|Radna]]\n* [[Razbor]]\n* [[Roga\u010dice]]\n* [[Rovi\u0161\u010de pri Studencu]]\n* [[Selce nad Blanco]]\n* [[\u0160entjan\u017e, Sevnica|\u0160entjan\u017e]]\n* [[\u0160entjur na Polju]]\n* [[\u0160kovec, Sevnica|\u0160kovec]]\n* [[Skrovnik]]\n* [[Slan\u010dji Vrh]]\n* [[Slap, Sevnica|Slap]]\n* [[\u0160mar\u010dna]]\n* [[Spodnje Mladeti\u010de]]\n* [[Spodnje Vodale]]\n* [[Srednik, Sevnica|Srednik]]\n* [[\u0160tajngrob]]\n* [[Str\u017ei\u0161\u010de, Sevnica|Str\u017ei\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Studenec, Sevnica|Studenec]]\n* [[Svinjsko]]\n* [[Tel\u010de]]\n* [[Tel\u010dice]]\n* [[Trnovec, Sevnica|Trnovec]]\n* [[Tr\u0161\u010dina]]\n* [[Tr\u017ei\u0161\u010de, Sevnica|Tr\u017ei\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Velika Hubajnica]]\n* [[Veliki Cirnik]]\n* [[Vranje, Sevnica|Vranje]]\n* [[Vrh pri Bo\u0161tanju]]\n* [[Vrhek]]\n* [[Zabukovje nad Sevnico]]\n* [[Zavratec, Sevnica|Zavratec]]\n* [[Zgornje Mladeti\u010de]]\n* [[Zgornje Vodale]]\n* [[\u017digrski Vrh]]\n* [[\u017dirovnica, Sevnica|\u017dirovnica]]\n* [[Znojile pri Studencu]]\n* [[\u017durkov Dol]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==Notable people==\nNotable people from the Municipality of Sevnica include the model [[Melania Knauss]], the handball player [[Matja\u017e Mlakar]], the historian [[Janko Prunk]] (from [[Loka pri Zidanem Mostu]]), and the writer [[Ludvik Mrzel]] (also from Loka pri Zidanem Mostu).\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[http://www.sevnica.si/ Sevnica.si]. Official page of the municipality.\n*[http://v1.geopedia.si/?params=L408_F110_T105_vF_b4_x520201.75_y96080.73000000001_s11 Municipality of Sevnica at Geopedia]{{Dead link|date=April 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} {{in lang|sl}}\n\n{{Geographic location\n | Centre = Sevnica\n | N  = [[Municipality of La\u0161ko|La\u0161ko]]\n | NE = [[Municipality of \u0160entjur|\u0160entjur]]\n | E  = [[Municipality of Kr\u0161ko|Kr\u0161ko]]\n | S  = [[Municipality of \u0160kocjan|\u0160kocjan]]\n | SW = [[Municipality of Mokronog-Trebelno|Mokronog-Trebelno]]\n | W  = [[Municipality of Litija|Litija]]<br/>[[Municipality of \u0160entrupert|\u0160entrupert]]\n | NW = [[Municipality of Rade\u010de|Rade\u010de]]\n}}\n{{Sevnica}}\n{{Municipalities of Slovenia}}\n\n[[Category:Municipality of Sevnica| ]]\n[[Category:Municipalities of Slovenia|Sevnica]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Styria (Slovenia)|Sevnica]]\n[[Category:1994 establishments in Slovenia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Municipality of Sevnica\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Sevnica''\n| native_name_lang        = sl<!-- ISO 639-2 code e.g. \"fr\" for French. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = 2